Package: cards
Title: Analysis Results Data
Version: 0.0.0.9019
Authors@R: c(
    person("Daniel D.", "Sjoberg", , "danield.sjoberg@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0862-2018")),
    person("Becca", "Krouse", , "becca.z.krouse@gsk.com", role = "aut"),
    person("F. Hoffmann-La Roche AG", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
  )
Description: The package constructs Clinical Data Interchange Standards
    Consortium (CDISC) compliant Analysis Results Data objects. These
    objects are used and re-used to construct summary tables,
    visualizations, and written reports. The results may also be
    represented as JavaScript Object Notation (JSON) or Yet Another Markup
    Language (YAML) structures.
